		<li> <b>Operation Medic: </b> The medic of the team, a certified medical professional also trained in using the company's equipment, they don't need to be trained on RnD, but they
		probably are anyways, the medic has access to a great amount of devices and tools (courtesy of Veymed), to ensure the crew is up and running at all times </li>
		<li> <b> Operation Enforcer: </b> The operation enforcer is a member of the Space Police or a mercenary sent by them to both ensure the company is following it's policies correctly and
